{"type": "article", "id": 28212, "title": "扶手椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-15T06:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702161824eom9JdqtxL83vHCl.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>这个造型上并没有规则的白色扶手椅是设计毕业生 <a href=\"http://ikkionno.com/\">Caroline Eriksson</a> 的作品，曾在今年的米兰国际家具展上做过展出。Eriksson 在本应连接的地方采用了悬空的设计，同时保留了椅子的完整性，不对称的造型看上去相当大胆。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021618224a3DfsCt7vBSuiLj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161823Yly45FZ3BHdsiaoC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161823yimAP0Wx96c8h1U3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}